instructions: On your Android phone, open Datally. Open the menu, and tap Guest mode . Note: In Datally version 1.7 and earlier, find Guest mode on the home screen. Optional: Add password protection by tapping Include a password. Set the amount of data the guest can use. Tap Turn on guest mode . Set a password if enabled.
On your Android phone, open Datally. Tap Turn off guest mode . Enter the password if enabled.
